Text:
Very proud of what the Firenze team have all achieved this year - you guys have smashed it and ensured Firenze has had a breakout year, firmly establishing itself as the default Lombard solution for the wealth management market.

Behind the headline grabbing debt raises, equity raises, partner wins, team growth and loan book growth there are real stories of outcomes which matter most. Some of my highlights of 2025:

- The couple who couldn't get a mortgage due to their age realising they didn't need to sell all their investments to buy their retirement home;
- The woman who found her dream home but feared she was going to lose it if she was stuck in a chain and had too much CGT in her portfolio to use her assets but was fortunate her wealth manager worked with Firenze;
- The clients who stressed about losing a large part of their ISA allowance after taking money out of a flexisa but timings didnt quite work out for getting the money back in and found a solution through Lombard lending;
- The parents who gifted house deposits to their children without having to worry about losing access to their own assets;
- The advisor who had his biggest win of the year in a RFP against a private bank as he now had Lombard lending,
- The platform who won a huge new advisor relationship they had been prospecting for years and finally gave them an opportunity due to Lombard lending.

These are the outcomes that make a difference to people and massive thanks to not just the team but all our investors, partners, clients and friends who have helped make this a reality. 

Merry Xmas and all the best for 2026,
